result.name: Whole Genome Sequence of Indegenous Malaysian population
result.description: Whole Genome Sequence of 6 indigenous Malaysian population: Jehai (5 individuals), Seletar (4 individuals), MahMeri (1 individual), Jakun (1 individual), Dusun (2 individuals) and Mendriq (2 individuals) at 30x coverage by Illumina HiSeq2500
